@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our platform.</p>

<h2>2. Purpose</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Help users easily search for doctors and healthcare facilities.</li>
    <li>Optimize appointment scheduling to reduce wait times and improve healthcare experiences.</li>
    <li>Connect healthcare professionals with patients through transparent reviews and modern technology.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>User Registration Data:</strong> Name, email, phone number.</li>
    <li><strong>Patient Profile:</strong> Basic information, medical history, and health concerns.</li>
    <li><strong>Doctor Profile:</strong> Qualifications, specialty, experience, working hours, and affiliations.</li>
    <li><strong>Search Preferences:</strong> Search history for doctors and medical institutions.</li>
    <li><strong>Appointments:</strong> Scheduled, modified, or canceled appointments.</li>
    <li><strong>Reviews & Ratings:</strong> User feedback after consultations.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account Management:</strong> To create and manage user accounts.</li>
    <li><strong>Doctor & Facility Search:</strong> To help users find healthcare professionals.</li>
    <li><strong>Appointment Booking:</strong> To schedule, modify, or cancel appointments.</li>
    <li><strong>Review & Feedback System:</strong> To display transparent ratings and comments.</li>
    <li><strong>Medical Records:</strong> Securely store and share patient history.</li>
    <li><strong>Health Content:</strong> Provide information on diseases, prevention, and treatment.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Data Security</h2>
<p>We use encryption and secure storage systems to protect personal data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.</p>

<h2>6. User Rights</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Access and update personal information.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of accounts.</li>
    <li>Control visibility of reviews and feedback.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell or share personal data except with:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Healthcare providers</strong> (when booking an appointment).</li>
    <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> (if required by law).</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Users will be notified of any significant changes.</p>

<p>For any concerns or questions, please contact our support team.</p>
